OOC: Dude, Symphony is a MALE, a GUY!!!  This better not turn out like the
Fenox incident*glares at Yanshosh very evilly*

::Symphony::

      Symphony is hit by the blasts, and goes flying backwards again.

       "Ugh..." He mumbles in pain.

         Symphony was no longer in good battle condition, he was bleeding
all over.  Symphony ran into the CF as quick as his legs could carry him,
and then he ran to a CR.

        "Got...to....heal," He said, walking to the CR and going into
healing process.
